				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/B%E1%BA%A5t-ki%E1%BA%BFn-tri%C3%AAu-thu%E1%BB%B3-l%E1%BB%99/poem-zoGudUwl45_4cRRJKhGyHA">Bất kiến triêu thuỳ lộ - 不見朝垂露</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/Ch%E1%BB%AD-h%E1%BA%A3i-ca/poem-Bxnx7qx0Jg5ENQvxundFfQ">Chử hải ca - 煮海歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/author-ODOFEl8xHVsWXQUPgj9Ktg">Liễu Vĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-kh%E1%BB%91c-th%E1%BB%AD/poem-zoqxnqSFTPrE2zeh9IBnRA">Hạ nhật khốc thử - 夏日酷暑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-thu%E1%BB%B5-kh%E1%BB%9Fi/poem-5pBTW1x8JDnClVz-00vALg">Hạ nhật thuỵ khởi - 夏日酷暑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/H%E1%BB%B7-v%C5%A9/poem-e2My-kSGhRc64YCHk_gJ7Q">Hỷ vũ - 喜雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-ng%C5%A9-th%E1%BB%A7-II-k%E1%BB%B3-4-M%C3%A3nh-h%E1%BB%95-b%E1%BA%B1ng-k%E1%BB%B3-uy/poem-bLniyDSmmcKl6enXhnrcTA">Khiển hứng ngũ thủ (II) kỳ 4 (Mãnh hổ bằng kỳ uy) - 遣興五首其四（猛虎憑其威）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-c%C3%BAc-thu%E1%BB%B7-nguy%E1%BB%87t-t%E1%BA%A1i-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-YCX3i6Ujl0-4PFgEYq_QRg">Phú đắc cúc thuỷ nguyệt tại thủ kỳ 2 - 賦得掬水月在手其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Thu%E1%BB%B7-c%E1%BB%91c-d%E1%BA%A1-h%C3%A0nh-k%C3%BD-T%E1%BB%AD-M%E1%BB%B9-Th%C3%A1nh-Du/poem-FFz1vwSnqt3-FS9BXxREFQ">Thuỷ cốc dạ hành ký Tử Mỹ, Thánh Du - 水谷夜行寄子美聖俞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Tr%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-0FUoqqh7D8aLj4boJLIO_w">Trừ tịch - 除夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%91%C4%83ng-hoa/poem-IYiVva8suurlhkrMYB0iQw">Vịnh đăng hoa - 詠燈花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
